  <scopecontent id="aspace_31dbe3063ee70b9f543f44a4b9865dcb">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Subject files concerning fertilizer, milk products, and advertising; financial reports; minutes; alphabetical files, many of Henry W. Jeffers III, vice president of the company, including appointment calendars, cash payments and receipts, payrolls, reports, photographs, and other records.</p>  </scopecontent>
